001package gbw.melange.common.events.observability;
002
003/**
004 * <p>IFallibleBiConsumer interface.</p>
005 *
006 * @author GustavBW
007 * @version $Id: $Id
008 */
009@FunctionalInterface
010public interface IFallibleBiConsumer<T> extends UndeterminedBiConsumer<T> {
011
012    /**
013     * <p>accept.</p>
014     *
015     * @param old a T object
016     * @param newer a T object
017     * @throws java.lang.Exception if any.
018     */
019    void accept(T old, T newer) throws Exception;
020}
